data.description: Location, Location, Location This beautiful home boasts a master bedroom, 1 and a half baths with a laundry area, spacious kitchen, and living room on the first floor.  The second floor boasts 2 spacious bedrooms. the outdoor space includes a covered deck and a partially fenced yard and patio area giving you lots of room to entertain your guests. This charming home is conveniently located near the hospital, restaurants, shopping center, and town. Bring your imagination to put your finishing touches and make this your dream home.
